        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:08.500",
        "end": "00:10.500",
        "original": "おしゃれですね、かっこいい！",
        "english": "It's so stylish! So cool!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:10.900",
        "end": "00:13.000",
        "original": "そして、本日24時ですね、",
        "english": "And today at midnight,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:13.000",
        "end": "00:14.500",
        "original": "12月2日の0時に",
        "english": "at 0:00 AM on December 2nd,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:14.500",
        "end": "00:17.300",
        "original": "デジタルリリースが開始されますので、",
        "english": "the digital release will begin!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:17.800",
        "end": "00:20.900",
        "original": "ライブに向けて、たくさん聴いてくれよな！",
        "english": "So listen to it a lot for the live!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:21.000",
        "end": "00:23.900",
        "original": "や、もうコールできるところいっぱいだからね！",
        "english": "Yeah, there are so many parts to call out to!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:24.000",
        "end": "00:26.500",
        "original": "めちゃめちゃ、もうライブのための曲だから！",
        "english": "Seriously, this song was made for the live!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:26.700",
        "end": "00:30.800",
        "original": "エクステ！エクステ！エクステ！",
        "english": "Exte! Exte! Exte!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:30.900",
        "end": "00:33.500",
        "original": "お前ら新曲いっぱい聴いて、",
        "english": "You guys listen to the new song a lot,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:33.500",
        "end": "00:36.600",
        "original": "予習して、ライブ楽しみにして待っててほしい！",
        "english": "study up, and look forward to the live!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:36.700",
        "end": "00:40.800",
        "original": "そしてアルバム『シークレットオーダー』を持って...",
        "english": "And bring our album, 'Secret Order'...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:40.900",
        "end": "00:43.000",
        "original": "持って？持って？持って？",
        "english": "Bring it? Bring it? Bring it?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:43.100",
        "end": "00:46.000",
        "original": "奪われないように気をつけてね！持ってね！",
        "english": "Be careful it doesn't get stolen! Bring it!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:46.100",
        "end": "00:48.500",
        "original": "ライブ来てね！運ばなきゃ！",
        "english": "Come to the live! We gotta carry it!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:48.500",
        "end": "00:51.500",
        "original": "オッケー！聴いて予習してね！",
        "english": "Okay! Listen and study up!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:51.600",
        "end": "00:54.500",
        "original": "アルバムは、えっと、22時から販売開始！",
        "english": "The album starts selling at, uh, 10:00 PM!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:54.600",
        "end": "00:56.500",
        "original": "もう一分もない！早い！",
        "english": "Not even a minute left! So fast!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:56.500",
        "end": "00:57.600",
        "original": "みんな買ってね！",
        "english": "Everyone, please buy it!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:57.700",
        "end": "00:59.500",
        "original": "ホロックスのみんな！",
        "english": "HoloX fans!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:59.800",
        "end": "01:02.500",
        "original": "え、本当に4年間ありがとう！",
        "english": "Um, really, thank you for these 4 years!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:02.600",
        "end": "01:05.900",
        "original": "付いてきてくれてありがとう！",
        "english": "Thank you for following us!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:06.000",
        "end": "01:08.500",
        "original": "来年はもうホロックスの、",
        "english": "Next year will be",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:08.500",
        "end": "01:11.000",
        "original": "我々の年にしていくので、頑張ろうね！",
        "english": "HoloX's year, our year, so let's do our best!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:11.100",
